│ ```bash                                                                                                                                                                                  │
│ perl -0777 -pe 's/InsElt = II;\nif \(InsElt\) \{\n  if \(auto IP = Builder\.GetInsertPoint\(\); IP != II->getIterator\(\)\)\n    II->moveBefore\(&\*IP\);\n}/InsElt = II;\nif (InsElt)   │
